# How to Change and Display Units of Measurement

## Reference
- [How to Change and Display Units of Measurement in BLENDER (Micro Tip)](https://youtu.be/oWseWAoeMls?si=0h7kGnp_20OxoyPz), Brandon's Drawings

## Change units of measurement
- Scene properties > Units > Unit System
    - None ("Blender" units)
    - Metric (metric system)
    - Imperial (feet, inches)
    - etc

## Display measurements
- Overlays menu
    - Measurements (near the bottom)
        - Toggle on and off four measurements
            - Edge Length
            - Edge Angle
            - Face Area
            - Face Angle